high_descs: Turn right and go forward to the counter to the left of the stove.
Take the left spoon that is on the counter.
Turn left and go forward and to the brown shelf on the wall straight ahead.
Place the spoon in the white mug on the shelf.
Pick up the mug off the shelf.
Turn right and go to the counter left of the stove.
Place the mug on the counter under the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Put a spoon in a mug on a counter.

high_descs: Turn right and begin walking across the room,  hang a left before the oven and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the metal spoon that is to the left of the phone on the counter.
Turn left and walk over to the wooden shelving unit against the far wall.
Put the metal spoon into the white mug that is on the top shelf of the wooden shelving unit.
Pick up the white mug with the metal spoon inside it.
Turn around and walk back over to the kitchen counter to the left of the oven.
Place the white mug with the spoon inside onto the counter just below of the metal spoon that is already on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a white mug with a spoon inside onto the counter.

high_descs: Go right and stand in front of the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the spoon from the counter.
GO to the left and stand in front of the brown shelves.
Put the spoon in the white cup on the shelf.
Pick the white cup up from the shelf.
Go right and then right again to stand in front of the counter to the left of the stove.
Put the cup down on the right side of the counter, close to the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a spoon on the counter.
